leads.lead_text: Leaves somewhat keeled below; flowers on pedicels 2–6 mm long; sepals and petals similar in size and shape; hypanthium obconical, faintly 5-ribbed; Grampians only
Leaves not keeled below; flowers on pedicels to 1 mm long; sepals larger than petals; hypanthium cylindric, prominently 10-ribbed; Gippsland only
